### **The Algorithm That Kills**

**[ERIC_LOOMIS]** **[COMPAS_ALGORITHM]** **[RISK_ASSESSMENT]** **[SIX_YEAR_SENTENCE]** **[TRADE_SECRET]**

In **[2016]**, **[ERIC_LOOMIS]** was sentenced to **[SIX_YEARS_IN_PRISON]** based partly on a **["RISK_ASSESSMENT"]** algorithm called **[COMPAS]** that labeled him **["HIGH_RISK"]** for reoffending. **[LOOMIS]** never learned what **[DATA]** the algorithm used or how it calculated his **[SCORE]** - the company claimed their **[FORMULA]** was a **["TRADE_SECRET"]**. But **[INVESTIGATIVE_REPORTING]** later revealed that **[COMPAS]** systematically labeled **[BLACK_DEFENDANTS]** as **["HIGH_RISK"]** at nearly **[TWICE_THE_RATE]** of **[WHITE_DEFENDANTS]**, even when controlling for **[CRIMINAL_HISTORY]** and other factors.

**[ALGORITHM_SENTENCING]** **[BLACK_DEFENDANTS]** **[WHITE_DEFENDANTS]** **[TWICE_THE_RATE]** **[CRIMINAL_HISTORY]** **[CONTROLLING_FACTORS]**

The **[ALGORITHM]** wasn't malfunctioning. It was working exactly as designed - **to provide [TECHNOLOGICAL_JUSTIFICATION] for the same [RACIAL_TARGETING] that has operated for centuries**, while hiding that targeting behind claims of **[OBJECTIVE]**, **[DATA_DRIVEN_DECISION_MAKING]**.

**[ALGORITHM_FUNCTIONING_AS_DESIGNED]** **[TECHNOLOGICAL_JUSTIFICATION]** **[RACIAL_TARGETING]** **[CENTURIES_OF_OPERATION]** **[OBJECTIVE_CLAIMS]** **[DATA_DRIVEN_DECISION_MAKING]**

This is how **[CONTROL_MECHANISMS]** evolve: **the same [ESSENTIAL_FUNCTIONS] of containing and suppressing [BLACK_COMMUNITIES] adapt to use whatever tools and justifications are available**, from **[SLAVE_CODES]** to **[JIM_CROW_LAWS]** to **["COLORBLIND"]** policies to **[AI_ALGORITHMS]**. The **[TECHNOLOGY_CHANGES]**, but the **[SYSTEMATIC_TARGETING_CONTINUES]**.

**[CONTROL_MECHANISMS_EVOLUTION]** **[ESSENTIAL_FUNCTIONS]** **[BLACK_COMMUNITY_CONTAINMENT]** **[BLACK_COMMUNITY_SUPPRESSION]** **[TOOLS_AND_JUSTIFICATIONS_ADAPTATION]** **[SLAVE_CODES]** **[JIM_CROW_LAWS]** **[COLORBLIND_POLICIES]** **[AI_ALGORITHMS]** **[TECHNOLOGY_CHANGES]** **[SYSTEMATIC_TARGETING_CONTINUES]**

Understanding **[CONTROL_MECHANISMS]** through the **[DIGNITY_LENS]** reveals not just the specific tactics used to limit **[BLACK_AGENCY]** and **[RESISTANCE]**, but how those tactics adapt when challenged, how they connect across different institutions, and most importantly, how communities can recognize and counter them effectively.

**[DIGNITY_LENS]** **[SPECIFIC_TACTICS]** **[BLACK_AGENCY_LIMITATION]** **[RESISTANCE_LIMITATION]** **[TACTICS_ADAPTATION]** **[INSTITUTIONAL_CONNECTIONS]** **[COMMUNITY_RECOGNITION]** **[EFFECTIVE_COUNTERING]**

